Type: Package
Package: Shearwater
Title: Analyze Wedge-Tailed Shearwater Movement and Fisheries Overlap
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Cooper Owen
Maintainer: Cooper Owen <coopernowen@berkeley.edu>
Description: Provides tools for cleaning GPS tracking data, segmenting trips, calculating movement metrics, and analyzing fisheries overlap for wedge-tailed shearwaters.
